      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve honestly gotta see this beauty in person to believe it! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since day one, and it looks just like it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been kept tucked away in a garage, sparkles inside and out, and drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m so sad to see it go, but it\u2019s ready for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. Give me a shout if you want to come check it out\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
