    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a pinnacle of naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a meticulously maintained dual-VANOS system for linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. This example features the desirable 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. Mechanically, the vehicle is flawless: the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed as preventative maintenance. The suspension architecture remains tight, utilizing OEM components to preserve the original handling dynamics. The exterior showcases original paint with deep luster, while the cockpit features pristine Nappa leather and functional electronics. This is a turn-key collector-grade vehicle for the discerning enthusiast.",
